\c 3
\s Mwari ndiye murwiri panjodzi Pisarema raDhavhidhi panguva yokutiza kwake Abhusaromu mwanakomana wake.
\p
\v 1 Haiwa Jehovha, vadzivisi vangu vawanda sei! Vazhinji vanondimukira.
\v 2 Vazhinji variko vanoti kumweya wangu, Haano ruponeso kuna Mwari.
\v 3 Asi imwi Jehovha muri nhovo yangu kumativi ose; Kudzo yangu, nomusimudzi womusoro wangu,
\v 4 Ndinodana kuna Jehovha nenzwi rangu, Iye anondipindura ari pagomo rake dzvene.
\v 5 Ndakavata pasi ndikabatwa nehope; Ndikamuka; nekuti Jehovha anonditsigira.
\v 6 Handingatyi zviuru zvamazana zvavanhu, Vakandikomberedza kuzorwa neni.
\v 7 Simukai, Jehovha; ndirwirei, Mwari wangu; nekuti makarova vavengi vangu vose pashaya dzavo; Makavhuna meno avakaipa.
\v 8 Ruponeso runobva kuna Jehovha; Kukomborera kwenyu ngakuve pamusoro pavanhu venyu.
